# AI QA / Evaluation Lab — Comprehensive Gap Analysis & Development Plan

## Executive Summary

I've read all 6 specification documents (PRD, TRD, App Flow, UI/UX, Backend Schema, Implementation Plan) and every line of code across **~80 files** in the codebase. The app has a **solid foundation** — the Prisma schema covers all 20+ tables, auth flows work, services exist for all core domains, API routes are wired up, and the evaluate worker processes background jobs. However, the app is **~40% complete** relative to what the documents specify. The UI pages are almost entirely **read-only server-rendered displays** with no interactive client-side behavior. Below is a precise, document-backed gap analysis.

