## What's Missing — Feature by Feature

### 🔴 CRITICAL: UI is Read-Only / No Client Interactivity

This is the **#1 systemic issue**. Every page renders server-side data, but **none of the buttons actually do anything**. All forms and buttons are inert HTML elements with no `onClick`, no form `action`, no API calls.

| Page | Buttons That Don't Work |
|---|---|
| **Prompts** | "New Version" button — no modal/form to create a prompt version. "Compare" button — no diff viewer. Provider/model/temp selects — no state. Editor textarea — no save action. No publish/archive buttons |
| **Datasets** | "Import CSV" button — no file upload flow. "Add Case" button — no modal. "Run Dataset" button — no action |
| **Runs** | "Start Run" button — no action. Run builder selects — no state/options populated from DB. "Queue Evaluation" — dead. "Retry Failed" — dead. "Cancel" — dead. "Export" — not wired |
| **Traces** | No span click-to-expand. No trace selection. No compare view. Timeline items are not clickable |
| **Grading** | Review sliders — no submission. "Needs Fix" / "Approve" buttons — dead. No auto-grade trigger |
| **Comparisons** | No way to create a new comparison report from the UI. "Approve Release" not present |
| **Analytics** | Audit log screen missing entirely. Search across entities not wired |
| **Settings** | No workspace member management UI. No billing/Stripe integration UI. No API key management. No model defaults editor |
| **Dashboard** | Onboarding checklist items are not interactive/tracked |
| **App Shell** | Mobile hamburger menu doesn't open. Search bar is display-only. Workspace switcher doesn't switch |

